# Root-level agent scratch & one-off build artifacts — keep local, never commit to main
# (issue #110/#60 build hygiene). Root-anchored so real modules under ArkLib/
# (e.g. ArkLib/ProofSystem/RingSwitching/Scratch.lean) are unaffected.
/scratch/
/scratch*.lean
/scratch*.py
# Agent scratch tree under ArkLib/ — throwaway proof probes, never committed and
# excluded from the ArkLib.lean umbrella (keeps update-lib.sh / check-imports.sh green).
/ArkLib/Scratch/
/patch*.py
/*_err.txt
/full_file.txt
/.tmp_*

# Vendored / scratch artifacts (review-only; not part of the repo content)
# Reference PDFs (ABF26 + cited works), see references/MANIFEST.md if vendored.
*.pdf
# Ad-hoc review / inspection notes (claude_review.md, codex_review.md,
# *_REVIEW*.md, CL_PR_COMMENT.md, CL_PR_COMMENTS_*.md, PRnnn_PR_COMMENT.md).
claude_review.md
codex_review.md
*_REVIEW*.md
CL_PR_COMMENT*.md
CL_REVIEW_*.md
CD_REVIEW_*.md
TOYPROBLEM_REVIEW.md
PR[0-9]*_REVIEW*.md
PR[0-9]*_INLINE_COMMENTS.md
PR[0-9]*_PR_COMMENT*.md
# Downloaded HTML / paper dumps
*.html
"VEIL — Formal Verification Audit_files/"
references/

